name: Lil Bob
description: The SpongeBob character in the picture is depicted with a bold and flashy appearance. He is wearing a dark green pinstripe suit with a matching hat that features a camouflage-patterned band. SpongeBob has a smug, confident expression with his mouth showing a diamond-encrusted grill, emphasizing a wealthy and luxurious persona. He is holding a stack of cash in one hand and making a gesture with his other hand, displaying a large, extravagant ring. This portrayal gives off a vibe of opulence and swagger, as if he is styled as a cartoon version of a wealthy, flashy figure.
